OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPressure grows for ban on  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnew leasehold flats        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government is facing growing calls 
OL,6, to ban new leasehold flats in England  
OL,7, and Wales.                             
OL,9,FIt has said a ban on the sale of new   
OL,10,Fleasehold houses will be added to a    
OL,11,Fbill, which has been introduced to     
OL,12,FParliament, as soon as possible.       
OL,14,FBut Minister Baroness Penn said        
OL,15,Fabolishing leasehold for flats was     
OL,16,F"more complicated" and reforms would be
OL,17,Ftaken forward at a later date.         
OL,19,FCampaigners, Labour and some Tories    
OL,20,Fwant leasehold to be scrapped entirely.
